  "original_title": "\u0b95\u0bbe\u0bb2\u0bbf\u0bae\u0bc1\u0b95\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbf\u0b9f\u0bb2\u0bcd \u0baa\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bbe\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bae\u0bcd \u0bae\u0bc0\u0ba4\u0bc1 \u0b85\u0b9f\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1\u0bae\u0bc1\u0bb1\u0bc8 : \u0b95\u0ba9\u0b9f\u0bbe, \u0baa\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bbe\u0ba9\u0bbf\u0baf\u0bbe \u0b95\u0ba3\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0ba9\u0bae\u0bcd",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Crackdown on vacating protest: Canada, Britain condemn",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "Britain and Canada have expressed their deep concern and condemnation of the action taken against the demonstrators in front of the Presidential Secretariat at midnight in Colombo's Kalimaguttal area.",
        "I am very concerned about the news coming from the empty-faced protest field. We reiterate the importance of the right to peaceful protest, said British High Commissioner Sarah Hulten.",
        "I don't know why this is happening in an empty protest field. The Canadian High Commissioner said it was important for officers to act with restraint and avoid violence."
      ],
